title: Welcome to Zombozo-Zone!
description: During medieval times, Team Tennyson must fight to remember that they're not in the past at all, but actually at a Renaissance-esque faire, where "King Zombozo" has hypnotized its guests into thinking they live in the past!

title: Ain't That a Kick in the Side?
description: After Witch Way teases Prohyas by calling him, "Vambre's sidekick," Prohyas intensifies his efforts to prove them wrong.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 1
description: While Windblade is away on a mission, Bee decides to relive a fun memory.

title: Suerte
description: When Vic cheats on an enchanted board game, the malevolent characters come to life, and it's up to V & V to figure out how to put them back in the game.

title: Block Party
description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

title: Pancake's Bus Tour
description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

title: Omni-Copped
description: When Grandpa Max's engineer buddy Phil Billings gifts Team Tennyson the Omni-Copter, a state of the art flying vehicle that can transport the Rustbucket for overseas adventures, Steam Smythe takes to the skies to ground Ben and company's first test flight; but unbeknownst to our heroes, Smythe was sent to battle Ben's latest alien forms by a mysterious, powerful enemy: the Forever Knight.

title: La princesa de jade
description: A raíz de un cruel ataque al Palacio, Los Hijos de Garmadon roban la segunda Máscara Oni, y los ninjas invitan a la Princesa Real, Harumi, a su improvisada familia.

title: Candy Is Dandy/Catastrophe
description: Candy Is Dandy: When the Mayor gives the girls some candy in gratitude for saving the day, they become hooked on the stuff. They even make a deal with a local villain to commit crimes for treats./Catastrophe: A monster is frantically tearing up the town looking for his lost kitty. But in a city the size of Townsville, how can the girls find one lone cat?

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Memory Part 1
description: Windblade tries to help Bumbleebee but he is wary of this "stranger".

title: Tunnels
description: The Bears discover a network of tunnels underneath the cave. Are they prepared to discover where they lead to and who dug them?

title: Creek Cart Racers
description: A high-speed race with a high-stakes prize may be too much for Craig and his friends.

title: Loteria
description: Cuando Vic hace trampa en un juego de mesa encantado, los malvados personajes cobran vida, y V y V son los responsables de averiguar cómo volver a ponerlos en el juego.

title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

title: El chillido de hombre muerto
description: La casi desaparición de Zane a manos del Señor "E" obliga a los ninjas a huir a bordo del Bounty, donde descubren que una tramisión que Zane interceptó puede revelar la ubicación oculta del "Silencioso".

title: Fixing a Flonk
description: Wanting to stop Flonk from being an evildoer for good, Prohyas tries to find Flonk a permanent venue for his nasty comedy. Vambre, however, wants to deliver him to the cops as usual.

title: The Hard Easy
description: A delicate race of frog people employ Finn & Jake to help them deal with Prince Huge, an evil lizard creature who's ravaging the moss swamp.

title: Attack the Block Party
description: Clarence, Jeff and Sumo investigate a high school party down the street, which they mistake for an alien invasion.

title: Cambio de Temporada
description: Cuando nuestros héroes regresan de sus vacaciones, K.O. se horroriza al descubrir que las cosas cambiaron.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Stratified/Maze Daze
description: Stratified: The AO embark on a mission into the mysterious labyrinth world of Vestroia to find Strata the Hunter and free the Bakugan he has imprisoned./Maze Daze: Lost in the maze of Vestroia the AO encounter powerful forces that seem to be struggling for control over the alien landscape.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Neighborhood Grill
description: Clarence is so troubled by the sight of his teacher in a social setting outside of school, he can't stop himself from intruding on her doomed blind date.

title: A Fistful of Brains
description: Grandpa Max and Rook are looking all over the galaxy for Ben, who is trapped on Khyber's hidden personal hunting preserve.

title: The Future
description: Gumball, Darwin and Banana Joe investigate Banana Barbara's mysterious disappearance and uncover an old rival's shadowy scheme in the process.

title: Bichos
description: Cuando Unikitty y la banda descubren un bicho asqueroso en el castillo, están desesperados por deshacerse de él para siempre, pero Unikitty se niega a permitir que lo aplasten, no importa qué tan asqueroso o peligroso parezca. ¿Qué tipo de red está tejiendo Unikitty para sus amigos?

title: Teletraan X Part 2
description: Investigating a signal in an abandoned missile silo, Bee and Windblade discover their computer back up drone Teletraan X, but it's a trap!

title: I Love You Mao Mao
description: An explosive loner and his slacker best friend are waylaid from their journey into legend, only to find that their story is just beginning.

title: Dr. Animo and the Mutant Ray
description: Dr. Animo has broken out of jail, and has been tracking down Ben, intent on revenge. At the same time, Ben's broken off a piece of the Omnitrix, and as a result, has turned into weird alien combinations, i.e. StinkArms.

title: El cuarto oscuro
description: Tras ser rechazado por un club de fotografía, Val intenta conseguir una foto del legendario Chupacabra para demostrar su valor.

title: Game of Masks
description: As Lloyd and Harumi search the Oni Temple for the last mask, the ninja are taken hostage and discover Princess Harumi's true intentions.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 1
description: With Windblade captured by the Seekers, Bumblebee is on his own for the first time and is responsible for saving Cybertron.

title: The Mummy's Curse
description: The Baby Bears must return a mummy to its tomb or else they'll be cursed forever.

title: Back to the Library
description: Uncle Grandpa uses time travel to convince his past self to return a library book on time.

title: True Potential
description: Just when the Ninja think they have saved the day, Lord Garmadon returns to Ninjago, and frees Harumi, who encourages him to "achieve his true potential" by conquering the one thing that has always stood in his way, his son, Lloyd.

title: Innervasion Part 3: Strange Bedfellows
description: After the Junkbot shoots the Omnitrix and it begins glowing neon-blue, an imprisoned Vilgax explains it is now a gateway through which the Fulmini Empire will invade Earth, but the only way to stop them is from within the Omnitrix, so Ben must team up with the ultimate baddie if he is to save his planet.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Episodio 200 Super Indulgente y Espectacular: Parte 2
description: Los Titanes descubren lo difícil que es producir dibujos animados cuando hacen uno sobre Michael y Aaron.

title: R & Arr
description: It's Lazy Sunday, and Unikitty and Puppycorn are having such an amazing time hanging out on the couch, they never want to move! Richard insists they have chores to do, but they're unwilling to let Lazy Sunday end. The two go to ridiculous lengths to never leave the comfort of their sofa, rowing it across the castle and like a ship and conscripting their friends to abandon their chores and join Lazy Sunday… no matter how dangerous and impossible it might become!

title: Suitable Armor
description: A veteran warrior insists that Vambre is under dressed for battle and takes it upon herself to garb Vambre in armor as Prohyas fights the beast solo without armor.

title: Ocarina
description: Fed up with Jake's antics, his son Kim Kil Whan takes action.

title: Cronicas de Mentiras Basquetboleras
description: Con la ayuda de Basketball, Oscar hace un tiro impresionante que le permite conseguir un lugar en la Liga Dorada.

title: Whiteout Part 2
description: Windblade flies to the Himalayas to investigate while Bee watches television, acquiring new verbal "samples".

title: #SweetJustice Part 4
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: 4 on 1
description: Onion's fear of crowds threatens his basketball team's success.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: El club de los solitarios
description: En lugar de celebrar el Día de San Valentín, Vic y Val se atreven a explorar una mansión encantada con sus rivales, Charlene y Piña.

title: El Ultimo robo
description: K.O. decide ayudar a Ginger a redescrubrir sus tiempos de gloria.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Hot Dog estrena su pelicula
description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

title: Lightfall Part 1
description: The mysterious Lord Obsidian calls Mega Man a traitor to robots and challenges him to a duel. An overconfident Mega Man is humbled by this mysterious new villain.

title: Innervasion Part 4: Mind over Alien Matter
description: While inside the Omnitrix, Ben and Vilgax must work together if they are to close the gateway, but once the Fulmini leader, the High Override, appears, even that might not be enough. Luckily, help arrives in the form of a being calling itself Glitch!

title: Curses/Bang for Your Buck
description: Curses: When Bubbles overhears the Professor saying some bad words, the girls add a whole new slew of adjectives to their vocabulary./Bang for Your Buck: When the girls and the Gangreen Gang discover a destructo ray for sale at Mojo's Yard Sale, each team sets out to see who can earn the most money and buy it first.

title: Show Don't Tell
description: Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max arrive at a Native American national park to witness the Ayasha Plinths, an ancient Stonehenge-like rock formation. But when the sinister sorcerer Hex arrives, Ben must battle against a beast Hex magically made out of huge rocks!

title: Band of Outsiders
description: A gang of streetwise kids takes Baby Ice Bear under their wing.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Punos Fuertes
description: Harto de perder cuando juega a los videojuegos contra su padre, Craig busca entrenarse en el Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: TV Knight 4
description: Batman and Commissioner Gordon go camping but instead of fun outdoor activities they'd rather watch TV.

title: Dead Man's Squall
description: Zane's near demise at the hands of Mr. E forces the ninja to flee aboard the Bounty, where they discover that a transmission Zane intercepted may reveal the hidden location of the Quiet One.

title: Magia Tragica
description: Cuando Richard monta un espectáculo de magia amateur, la Dra. Fox se obsesiona por descubrir cómo se hacen esos trucos que desafían la ciencia. Pero mientras se propone usar todo su intelecto para encontrar formas experimentales de hacer los trucos que vio en la fiesta del cachorro, ¿acaso arruinará accidentalmente el asombro de la magia?

title: El Poder de Dendy
description: Dendy y KO descubren una nueva y emocionante característica de las tarjetas de poder.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: El silencioso
description: Mientras que Lloyd y Harumi se aventuran a lo profundo de "Primeval's Eye" en busca de la tercer máscara Oni, los ninja tratan de arreglar al Bounty y hacer un descubrimiento sorprendente.

title: Computer Vampire
description: Oscar finds a mysterious old video game in the library.

title: Feeling Spacey
description: Oscar and Hedgehog arrive on a planet that has no emotions.

title: Four by Four
description: During their visit to Twin City, Ben and Gwen sign up for some Laser Town awesomeness, but when Ben is teamed up with Kevin, the two must overcome their differences if they are to end up on top!

title: Rush to Greatness
description: Rush puts his new battle upgrades to the test in a battle with Wave Man.

title: #SweetJustice Part 3
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Cleaning Day
description: Victor & Valentino gain a newfound respect for cleanliness after Chata's house traps them inside its labyrinth of ancient, magical walls.

title: Sabotage Part 2
description: Shockwave creates false memories designed to convince Bee he was always a Decepticon spy.

title: Space Emperor
description: When UG mistakes a kid in a costume for an evil space emperor, he sends him to another dimension where he becomes an actual evil space emperor and UG must figure out some way to bring him home.

title: TKO's House
description: TKO is getting restless.

title: Cool Bikes
description: Mordecai and Rigby want cool bikes because if their bikes are cool, then they are cool.

title: Bubblevicious/The Bare Facts
description: Bubblevicious: Bubbles is tired of people dismissing her as more sugar than spice. When she sets out to prove she's hardcore, she takes everyone by surprise, even Mojo Jojo./The Bare Facts: After Mojo kidnaps and blindfolds him, the Mayor has to rely on the girls' very different individual accounts of the crime to figure out exactly what happened.

title: Teletraan X Part 1
description: The Decepticon Armada is nearing Earth to seek the Allspark and are desperate for clues.

title: Dendy's Power
description: Dendy and KO discover a fun and exciting new POW Card exploit.

title: Don't Be An Icarus
description: Robin tries to tell some Greek myths but the other Titans give their own fractured versions instead.

title: Snake Jaguar
description: In order to join the Sons of Garmadon, Zane (aka Snake Jaguar) participates in a deadly motorcycle initiation race.

title: Stop Attacking the Plaza
description: Boxman must go 24 hours without attacking Lakewood Plaza Turbo.

title: Mud Is Thicker Than Water
description: Ben, Gwen and Cousin Lucy try to find out how Psyphon's thugs are getting Plumber technology.

title: Ninjago chico, problemas grandes
description: Los ninjas corres a salvar a Lloyd. Un Lord Garmadon más poderoso que nunca, crea una enorme estatua para ayudarlo a gobernar Ninjago y a derrotar a los ninjas.

title: Guar serpiente
description: Para unirse a Los Hijos de Garmadon, Zane (alias Jaguar Serpiente) participa en una carrera de iniciación mortal de motocicletas.

title: El Coleccionista
description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic pierde una de las preciadas monedas de Val, Val hace un trato con un misterioso coleccionista de antigüedades para reemplazarla, pero el trato tiene consecuencias terribles.

title: The Kid From 3030
description: The kids meet a mysterious kid from the future and try to help him complete his mission.

title: No lo digas y Hazlo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max llegan a un parque nacional nativo americano para conocer los plintos de Ayasha, una antigua formación rocosa parecida a la de Stonehenge. Pero cuando llega el siniestro hechicero Hex, iBen debe luchar contra una bestia que Hex hizo mágicamente con rocas enormes!

title: Cube Part 2
description: Windblade finds it hard to believe that Bee can't remember his favorite sport, Cube!

title: La Melancolia de Oscar y Erizo
description: Susie organiza el concurso anual de talentos, y todos los campistas compiten para ganar.

title: The Extinction Event Part 2
description: Shockwave orders the Seekers to help him create an extinction event and destroy all organic life on the planet.

title: Lonely Haunts Club
description: Instead of celebrating Valentine's Day, Vic & Val take on a dare to explore a haunted mansion with their rivals, Charlene & Pineapple.

title: Juego de mascaras
description: Mientras Lloyd y Harumi buscan el templo Oni para la última máscara, los ninjas son tomados como rehenes y descubren que verdaderas intensiones de la Princesa Harumi.

title: Morituri Te Salutamus
description: Finn and Jake are trapped in the arena of the Fight King and must face gladiators to set themselves free.

title: Sabotage Part 1
description: From his lab on Cybertron, Shockwave launches an attack on Bee's most vulnerable place...his memories.

title: Venthalla
description: Owen has his super ball confiscated and locked up in Chef's office. Duncan, seeing an opportunity to get help escaping the daycare, leads an away team into the vents to recover Owen's ball.

title: Minus Mini
description: When Mega Mini is kidnapped by Blasto Woman, Mega Man must track down his missing partner without the full use of his own systems.

title: Collection Infection
description: Having pared down their Magisword collection, the Warriors are forced into unconventional battle choices on a dangerous mission into the Deepest Darkest Woods.

title: The Journey Part 2
description: The Autobots are nearly out of Energon, so they land on a dark planet where they encounter subterranean creatures.

title: An American Benwolf in London
description: Ben and Rook are called to London England to investigate the Forever Knights' latest activities.

title: Siloed Part 1
description: Windblade is playing Cube on Cybertron with Bee when she realizes these are memories and she is still held captive by Slipstream.

title: Cube Part 1
description: Bee discovers a mysterious object in the stolen Decepticon shuttle.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 1
description: With the help of Teletraan- X, Bee and Windblade excavate an deactivated Autobot that looks like a dinosaur.

title: Perfect Day
description: Ben thinks he's having 'the perfect day' only to realize he's been put in a dream world by Enoch and the Forever Knights who are after the Omnitrix. Ben's "dream world" soon becomes a nightmare world, with Ben forced to live out his ultimate terror...being stuck at school! But with Max and Gwen's help, he's able to vanquish his nightmare foes and re-enter the real world where he takes down  Enoch...only to reveal an even more powerful knight...The Forever King.

title: Checkin' Out!
description: A trip to the supermarket has bizarre consequences.

title: Lost in the Supermarket
description: During a trip to the supermarket with his mom, Clarence discovers produce adventure and coupon intrigue in aisle five...and every other aisle.

title: Ramen
description: The Baby Bears help a struggling ramen chef perfect her ramen and save her shop.

title: Abate and Switch
description: When the JLA tries to stop the Brothers Djinn, the ghoulish trio are able to direct spells on our heroes by saying their names forcing them to disguise themselves as each other in order to foil the spells.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 2
description: Bumblebee doubts his abilities as he has to find the Ark to awaken Optimus and the Autobots.

title: El chico del 3030
description: Los niños conocen a un misterioso niño del futuro y tratan de ayudarlo a completar su misión.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Watch It!
description: The Powerpuff Girls are tasked with keeping a priceless gem safe from thieves.

title: Misfortune Cookie
description: After receiving an ominous fortune, Uncle Grandpa must snoop out whom among his friends is an enemy in disguise.

title: A Man Man for All Seasons
description: When a run-in with the Hoover Gang leaves Aki unable to transform into Mega Man, he must don a cheap costume and enlist the unlikeliest of sidekicks, Man Man!

title: Frenemies/Strata's Fear
description: Frenemies: Two new Bakugan Brawlers, Shun and Magnus, try out for the AO./Strata's Fear: The AO solve the mystery of a kid's missing Bakugan and meet a Bakugan Hunter named Strata.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 1
description: Bee, Windblade and Grimlock finally determine the location of the lost ship, the Ark.

title: The Self-Indulgent 200th Episode Spectacular! Part 1
description: When their world starts disappearing, the Titans must confront their creators.

title: El verdadero potencial
description: Justo cuando los ninjas piensan que han salvado el día, Lord Garmadon regresa a Ninjago, y libera a Harumi, quien lo anima a "alcanzar su verdadero potencial" conquistando lo único que siempre se interpuso en su camino, su hijo, Lloyd.

title: Maccadam's Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bee's memory must be coming back - they access the Hivemind and visit three different eras of Maccadam's.

title: Allspark Part 2
description: They search for clues as to the whereabouts of the Allspark and uncover another important memory!

title: Lost and Found
description: Mordecai and Rigby go get a wallet.

title: Dream Scheme/You Snooze, You Lose
description: Dream Scheme: The Sandman would like a little rest so he puts the world to sleep. The girls must battle him in his dreams to get things back to normal./You Snooze, You Lose: When the Amoeba Boys find Mojo's plan to destroy the Powerpuff Girls, the girls unwittingly help them build a machine for their own destruction.

title: #SweetJustice Part 2
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: La mascara del engano
description: Cuando un sindicato de criminals desconocido amenaza a la Familia Real, los ninjas son llamados de nuevo a la acción y deben proteger a la princesa real y un artefacto legendario que puede tener poderes sobrenaturales.

title: Man Up 4: The Donnyest Game
description: With Man-Boy on the loose, Donny must be prepared for anything.

title: La casita de TKO
description: T.K.O. se está poniendo inquieto.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: That Will Be All
description: Steven and the Gems make a daring escape!

title: Uncle Grandpa's Odd-yssey
description: Uncle Grandpa and the gang must retrieve Tiger from the pound before she's adopted out.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 2
description: Teletraan-X's scans reveal their old friend Grimlock, who is intent on finding the rest of his missing dinosaur friends.

title: Merry Moochmas
description: It's wintertime in Aberdale and Clarence is convinced his winter wish for snow in Arizona will come true! However, his classmate Belson along with his grumpy cousin Gary Mooch are a little tougher to convince.

title: Fractured Part 1
description: Windblade discovers Bumblebee in the desert on his own.

title: 4 a 1
description: El temor de Cebollín a las multitudes amenaza el éxito de su equipo de baloncesto.

title: Unikitty News!
description: You're watching the Unikingdom News Show Super Good Morning Time Program Action Information Show, a variety news program put on (badly) by Unikitty and the gang: Hawkodile does the weather, Puppycorn does sports despite knowing none of the rules, Dr. Fox puts on a fun science-y cooking segment that goes awry, and Richard wants this to stop. Unikitty's got some hard hitting reporting and a big scoop after the break, if the studio survives that long!

title: Face Fix
description: Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve help Mr. Gus try to get his face back to normal before an important photo shoot.

title: The Jade Princess
description: In the wake of a vicious attack upon the palace, the Sons of Garmadon steal the second Oni Mask, and the ninja invite the royal princess, Harumi, into their makeshift family.

title: This Is Not a Drill
description: Mega Man and Dr. Light must set aside a father-son disagreement to stop Drill Man from taking revenge on his own overbearing father.

title: Evil's Encore
description: Dr. Animo reminisces about when he once took control of the Plumber's HQ in Mount Rushmore. (Flashback episode.)

title: The Quiet One
description: As Lloyd and Harumi venture deep into Primeval's Eye in search of the third Oni Mask, the ninja attempt to fix the Bounty and make a startling discovery.

title: Beta
description: Steven and Amethyst visit some friends in the country but Amethyst isn't being herself.

title: It Was Them
description: Dr. Animo has escaped his Plumber prison, and Ben and Rook must track him down before he turns the world into his personal mutant ant farm! (Introducing Nemetrix alien Slamworm, Galvan Plumbers Blukic and Driba, Arctiguana, new Ben alien Crashhopper.)

title: Lil' Dimples
description: Thinking it's a way to reconnect with her father, Raven enters a beauty pageant.

title: Dinner Apart-y
description: Unikitty and Puppycorn are invited to Master Frown and Brock's apartment for a dinner party. But the two roommates are butting heads, and are anything but on the same page. Can Unikitty help Brock and Master Frown get back in harmony before the dinner party is ruined? Will Puppycorn figure out which door is the bathroom?

title: The End of Muscle Man
description: The guys want to help Muscle Man finish his bucket list.

title: A Licking Time Bomb
description: Owen and Noah unwittingly become cookie moguls and must hide the secret ingredient, which is Owen's spit from licking the sprinkles off the cookies.

title: Atrapa la Botella
description: Manzana y Cebollín inventan un nuevo juego que atrae una atención inesperada.

title: License to Punch
description: Hawkodile's caught by the Action Police for bodyguarding without an Action License. He's can't protect the kingdom or do anything rad until he does, but the test at the DMV (The Department of Mayhem and Violence) is for nerds! Forced to retire his gloves, Hawkodile struggles to live a life without punching, so Unikitty vows to help her friend contain his urge to be action-y and study for the test. But there's more to the test than meets the eye.

title: Siloed Part 2
description: Windblade manages to fight her way out when Slipstream is called away and she discovers Bee and Teletraan-X are there to help!

title: Galaxy Jest
description: Joker is abducted into space by Mongul to entertain Mongul's troops. Unless the Justice League can re-capture him in time, a Joker gas bomb will go off in Gotham threatening the city.

title: The Virus
description: Gumball thinks Teri is way too scared of germs, but one's coming after him, and it wants revenge.

title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben ser más astutos que un pato malvado que se apoderó del techo de su edificio.

title: Snow Way Out
description: Owen wants everyone to love his new snowsuit and envy him, but it's just not working out that way.

title: Licencia para Golpear
description: A Hawkodile lo atrapa la policía de acción por trabajar como guardaespaldas sin licencia de acción. No puede proteger el reino ni hacer nada radical hasta tener la licencia, ipero la prueba en el Departamento de Caos y Violencia es para los nerds! Obligado a quitarse los guantes, Hawkodile lucha por vivir una vida sin golpes, por lo que Unikitty promete ayudar a su amigo a contener su impulso de entrar en acción y a estudiar para la prueba. Pero la prueba consiste en algo más de lo que parece.

title: Introducing Kevin 11
description: At a local swap meet, Ben instead sets his sights on a Sumo Slammer collectible, but when Kevin takes it for himself, our hero must get it back by overcoming Kevin's secret weapon: an 11th alien!

title: #HateTriangle
description: When Hal's ex-girlfriend shows up at the Metropolis High homecoming game and goes love-ballistic as the villain Star Sapphire, Jessica begins to second-guess her own nonviolent tactics.

title: Buggin' Out
description: When Unikitty and the gang discover a gross bug in the castle, they desperately want it gone for good, but Unikitty refuses to allow them to squish it, no matter how icky or dangerous looking it is. What sort of web is Unikitty weaving for her friends?

title: The Silence
description: When Gumball and Darwin's conversation dries up, they worry that their friendship is coming to an end. They try to find ways to get the conversation flowing again, but nothing seems to work. Maybe they have just grown apart?

title: The Gym
description: The Bears go to the gym and get quite the work out.

title: The Voice
description: When Gumball and Darwin receive a scary email, everyone is a suspect... including themselves!

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 2
description: Bee remembers an early version of Megatron where he was a gladiatorial hero, but realizes how dangerous he became.

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 1
description: Windblade explains the threat of Megatron and the Decepticons to Bee.

title: Innervasion Part 2: Call the Dream Police
description: After defeating the Warbot and discovering Vilgax inside, Ben's "secret voices" only worsen and begin affecting his sleep, but once Gwen discovers a sleepwalking Ben using missing items from the campsite to create his own massive Junkbot, it is up to Ben to stop his own creation.

title: Seasons Change
description: When our heroes return from time off, KO is horrified to discover that things have changed.

title: Eruption Part 1
description: As the Autobots discover the Ark, they have to wake up their friends in this battle for the future.

title: Deje de Atacar el Plaza
description: Box-man debe pasar 24 horas sin atacar Lakewood Plaza Turbo.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: The Basketball Liaries
description: With the help from Basketball, Oscar makes an impressive shot that scores him a spot on the Gold League.

title: Power Punchers
description: Fed up with losing in video games to his Dad, Craig seeks training in the Creek.

title: Steven vs. Amethyst
description: Steven and Amethyst get competitive while training with Pearl.

title: Clarence and Sumo's Rexcellent Adventure
description: On a school trip to the Aberdale Natural History Museum, Clarence and Sumo check out the displays, goof around with the exhibits and even remove a tooth from the T-Rex display.

title: Under a Red Sun
description: Steppenwolf "boom tubes" Superman to a planet with a red sun in order to make the Man of Steel powerless. Somehow Batman and Big Barda have to locate the planet before Superman is destroyed.

title: The Journey Part 1
description: Bee accesses a memory from onboard the Ark on its journey from Cybertron to Earth.

title: The Dark Room
description: After getting rejected by a photography club, Val tries to get a picture of the legendary Chupacabra in order to prove himself.

title: The Collector
description: When Vic accidentally loses one of Val's prized coins Val makes a deal with a mysterious antiques collector to replace it, but the deal has terrible consequences.

title: Secret Book Club
description: Kelsey starts a super secret book club to introduce Craig and JP to the joys of reading.

title: The Void
description: When Gumball and Darwin investigate a missing classmate, they discover a far greater mystery . . . about Elmore. Gumball and Darwin start noticing small details around Elmore High that don't add up. They come to the conclusion that Molly has disappeared, even though nobody else remembers her ever having existed. Mr Small confirms their suspicions and tells them that things are not always what they seem in Elmore. They set off on a quest to rescue Molly in an alternate dimension, and soon need rescuing themselves!

title: Bottle Catch
description: Apple and Onion's favorite game attracts some unexpected attention.

title: Shadowstriker Part 1
description: Bee doubts his fighting abilities as he continually loses in practice to Windblade.

title: Donny
description: In an attempt to save a village, Finn and Jake rehabilitate Donny the Ogre, who's a real jerk.

title: Jextra Perrestrial
description: JP believes he may be from another planet, so Craig tries to help him make contact.

title: Vampiro de Computadora
description: Oscar encuentra un videojuego viejo y misterioso en la biblioteca.

title: Portable Toilet
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to get out of a portable toilet.

title: Kiki's Pizza Delivery Service
description: Steven saves Kiki from some delicious nightmares.

title: Episodio 200 Super Indulgente y Espectacular: Parte 1
description: Cuando su mundo comienza a desaparecer, los Titanes deben confrontar a sus creadores.

title: Whiteout Part 1
description: Bee remembers his escape pod from the Ark crashed in the snowy Himalayas.

title: Super Watermelon Island
description: Steven finds out what happened to all those sentient watermelons he created.

title: Sintiendose Especiales
description: Oscar y Erizo llegan a una planeta que no tiene emociones.

title: Allspark Part 1
description: Hiding from the Decepticons, Windblade use her Cityspeaker powers to search Bee's memory files.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Galactic Wonder
description: Wonder Woman has won student of the month at Super Hero High again!  As a special surprise Principal Waller has flown in Wonder Woman's mother, Queen Hippolyta, for a visit. Queen Hippolyta is not happy with what she finds and demands that Wonder Woman return to school at the island paradise of Themyscira. Hoping to take her mind off of her troubles with her mother Wonder Woman, Batgirl and Supergirl decide to investigate a strange electromagnetic anomaly. Their investigation leads them to the hideout of Lena Luthor where they discover a plot between her and Eclipso to transform the planet Earth into a new version of Gemworld!  The girls will have to split up to find the generators scattered around the planet and destroy them. They'll also have to overcome Lena's new breed of mood altering Kryptomites to save the day and convince Queen Hippolyta that Super Hero High is the best school for Wonder Woman!

title: Struck by Lightning
description: Muscle Man and High Five Ghost get struck by lightning and can't remember each other.

title: All Up in Your Drill
description: Duncan stages a small coup to oust Courtney as their official class firefighter so that he can wear the shiny firefighter helmet - until he smells smoke in the classroom and begs her to take her job back.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Eruption Part 2
description: Teletraan-X has to reboot the offline computer systems to wake up their Autobot friends and the ship while fighting the Deceptions.

title: Ghost the Boy
description: Oscar and Hedgehog befriend a ghost who can't remember who he is.

title: Origin of Species
description: Origin of Species, Part 1: Dan meets his partner Bakugan Drago for the first time and we learn about the incident that happened on Earth twelve years ago./Origin of Species, Part 2: Dan and friends win the Bakugan Battle, firmly establishing the Awesome Ones as our heroes and Bakugan Brawlers.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Big Trouble, Little NinjaGo
description: The ninja race to save Lloyd, as a more powerful-than-ever Lord Garmadon creates an enormous Colossi to help him rule Ninjago and defeat the ninja.

title: The Mask of Deception
description: When an unknown criminal syndicate threatens the Royal Family, the Ninja are called back into action and must protect the royal princess and a fabled artifact that may hold supernatural powers.

title: Blade of Grass
description: Finn and Jake decide it's time for Finn to get a new sword. Finn reluctantly buys a grass sword from a mysterious old man, but the sword turns out to be cursed! And unfortunately for our hero, all sales are final.

title: Fantasma, El Nino
description: Oscar y Erizo se hacen amigos de un fantasma que no recuerda quién es.

title: Shadowstriker Part 2
description: Through memory, Bee is shown some of his past triumphs, like rescuing Optimus from Shadowstriker.

title: For the Love of Narwhal
description: Vambre rejects Darlin' Narwhal Magisword as being unfit for battle, but when Prohyas trains and brings out its full potential, Vambre resorts to improper extremes to get it back.

title: The Extinction Event Part 1
description: Decepticons Shockwave and Shadowstriker arrive on Earth with a simple plan to find the Allspark.

title: Nuclear Family Values
description: Firestorm encounters the Nuclear Family, a misguided group of robots who resemble a '50's sitcom family. They intend on blowing up a nuclear power plant in order to create a home where no one can touch them and they hope to use Firestorm's power to help them.

title: #SweetJustice Part 1
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Cena Festiva
description: Unikitty y Puppycorn están invitados al apartamento de Master Frown y Brock para una cena. Pero los dos compañeros de casa no logran ponerse de acuerdo absolutamente en nada. ¿Puede Unikitty ayudar a Brock y al Master Frown a volver a estar en armonía antes de que la cena sea un desastre? ¿Y descubrirá Puppycorn cuál es la puerta del baño?

title: Oscar & Hedgehog's Melody
description: Susie holds the annual talent show that has the rest of the campers competing to win.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 2
description: Slipstream and her Seekers engage in battle as our heroes trek towards the Ark.

title: Power Outage
description: A ghoul known as Calythos possesses the Parasite in order to drain the Justice League of its powers and use that stolen strength to open a massive volcano.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 2
description: Bee finds himself on Velocitron with Hod Rod to have some fun but it turns into a nightmare as the Plague of Rust descends.

title: One Last Score
description: KO decides to help Ginger recapture her glory days.

title: Big Fat Alien Wedding
description: Ben and Gwen accompany Max to a wedding, which doesn't make Ben particularly happy, especially given the fact he has to wear a tux and learn how to dance. During the wedding it's revealed that the bride's parents are aliens while the groom's family are ex-Plumbers. It turns out the bride's parents are out to sabotage the wedding because of a long lasting feud with the Plumbers, and take action by demonstrating their destructive powers and causing deadly havoc. Ben, Max and Gwen enter the fray and not only save the day, but make sure the ceremony goes on as planned.

title: Dread on Arrival
description: The ninja appeal to the police commissioner of Ninjago in an effort to help save Lloyd and thwart Harumi's efforts to resurrect the evil Lord Garmadon.

title: El Paseo en Autobus de Pancake
description: Manzana y Cebollín suben a un autobús que da un tour guiado como parte de su plan para recuperar el zapato de Manzana.

title: Drama Bomb
description: The school play goes off the rails when the drama teacher interferes.

title: Mr. Moon/What's Wrong with Dan
description: Mr. Moon: Wynton finds a new Bakugan who proves difficult to control but things get more complicated when Col. Tripp seizes control of Trox./What's Wrong with Dan: With "Dan" behaving strangely toward the AO Lightning sniffs out the truth- an impostor!

title: Know it All
description: Courtney must go all day without correcting her friends which is hard because they do everything wrong!

title: Maccadam's Part 1
description: Bee and Windblade avoid an attack by Slipstream and Bee asks to go to Maccadam's!

title: Innervasion Part 1: Message in a Boxcar
description: As Team Tennyson prepares their boxcar for an upcoming race, Ben is hearing voices and is unable to go Upgrade to enhance his car, but once the race is interrupted by a mysterious Warbot, Ben must overcome the voices inside his head if he is to defeat the giant adversary.

title: The Self-Indulgent 200th Episode Spectacular! Part 2
description: The Titans discover how hard cartoons are to produce when they make one about Michael and Aaron.

title: Fractured Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bumblebee does not remember her and her mission to find the Allspark is critical.

title: Home, Sweet Homesick
description: When the Girls go to Camp, Blossom has a hard time leaving her schoolwork at home.

title: The Oni & the Dragon
description: While Princess Harumi adjusts to life with the ninja, Lloyd and Jay search for answers about the Oni Masks, while Cole and Zane attempt to infiltrate the Sons of Garmadon.

title: Terror llegando
description: Los ninjas recurren al comisionado de la policía de Ninjago en un esfuerzo por ayudar a salvar a Lloyd y frustrar los esfuerzos de Harumi de resucitar al malvado Lord Garmadon.

title: Dia de limpieza
description: Victor y Valentino adquieren un nuevo respeto por la limpieza después de que la casa de Chata los atrapa dentro de su laberinto de paredes antiguas y mágicas.

title: Career Opportunities/Punch the Clock
description: Career Opportunities: After defeating Magnus the AO get an offer of employment from a surprising source Philomena Dusk!/Punch the Clock: During a commercial to celebrate their joining the AAAnimus team Dan and the AO rebel before they sellout.

title: Sun Scream/City of Frownsville
description: Sun Scream: The girls get the ultimate sunburn and must try to fight crime despite their UV damage./The City of Frownsville: When the tearful Lou Gubrious sets a crying ray on Townsville, the girls must find a way to stop the tears before the town is flooded.

title: Memory Part 2
description: Windlbade and Bumblebee are attacked by Decepticons and she regains his trust.

title: Domingo de Flojos
description: Es domingo de pereza, iy Unikitty y Puppycorn la están pasando tan bien en el sofá que no quieren moverse nunca! Richard insiste en que tienen tareas por hacer, pero ellos no están dispuestos a dejar que termine el domingo de pereza. Los dos hacen todo lo posible para no salir nunca de la comodidad de su sofá, remando por el castillo como si estuvieran en un barco y reclutando a sus amigos para que abandonen sus tareas y se unan al domingo de pereza, isin importar qué tan peligroso e imposible puede llegar a ser!

title: El oni y el dragon
description: Mientras que la Princesa Harumi se adapta a la vida con los ninjas, Lloyd y Jay buscan respuestas sobre las máscaras Oni, mientras que Cole y Zane intentan infiltrarse en Los Hijos de Garmadon.
